data.description: Inviting four-bedroom, two-bath home with a single-car garage, built in 2011, nestled on a spacious lot measuring 50 x 146. This well-maintained residence showcases modern updates, including refreshed bathroom tiles and new kitchen cabinets. Features a huge backyard for endless possibilities with a covered patio for entertaining. Covered front porch for relaxation & extra concreted driveway for ample parking. Explore the perfect blend of comfort and style in this move-in-ready gem.
